text.tspan: This is your current available balance. If you just
sold a book for $50, then you will find that amount
available in your stud-E-wallet. You can use this
balance to quickly complete future purchases on
the platform, or withdrawal it at any point.
How does StudEtree protect my information?
We take the protection of your personal
information very seriously, and keep it safely
stored in our encrypted databases. Along with
your personal information, we collaborate closely
with our financial partners to ensure the highest
level of cyber security and protection of your
Why should I link my bank account?
Once you link your bank account, you will be able
to transfer funds directly to and from your personal
account, providing flexible alternatives to PayPal
Why does it take 3-5 days to transfer funds
to and from my bank account?
The delay you might encounter to receive funds is
caused by the processing and transfer times of your
bank. This, unfortunately, is out of our control.
